.name
LJP
.author
Khalid Aldoseri 
.version
1.01
.description
A program to print text files on an HP LaserJet printer.  Supports
landscape or portrait modes, use of any built-in font, automatic
downloading of soft fonts, extremely fast printing, one or two logical
pages on a single paper, multiple styles of page headers, adjustable page
length and width, user specified pitch and point of a font, selectable
margins and tab spacing, multiple copies, optional line numbers, and more.
